___NOTES___

Form Analytics Tracker (FormAssembly).

Injects a hosted runtime (form-analytics.js) and passes its settings through
window.faConfig. The runtime watches FormAssembly forms and pushes
view / start / step_N / submit / error events to the dataLayer.

BEFORE SUBMITTING TO THE COMMUNITY TEMPLATE GALLERY:
- Open this template in the GTM Template Editor, confirm categories on the Info
  tab, and tick "Agree to the Community Template Gallery Terms of Service".
- Re-export from the editor and commit that file as template.tpl (do not edit
  template.tpl by hand).
- Repo root must also contain metadata.yaml, an Apache-2.0 LICENSE (all caps),
  and README.md, on the main branch, with Issues enabled.

HOSTING:
- The default script URL is a version-pinned jsDelivr URL backed by the repo.
  The inject_script permission is scoped to https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/* .
- To self-host (e.g. first-party on your own domain), change the script URL
  field AND edit the inject_script permission to match, or injectScript is
  blocked at runtime.

CONSENT:
- requiredConsentGroups must match your CMP's category IDs. Empty = no gating.


